videos.headline: Harsin explains why he subbed Finley for Nix at QB
videos.description: Following the comeback victory against Georgia State, No. 23 Auburn's Bryan Harsin explains why he made the change from Bo Nix to TJ Finley at QB.

videos.headline: Finley comes off bench to save No. 23 Auburn
videos.description: Georgia State puts up 21 points in the second quarter, but QB TJ Finley leads the Tigers to a late fourth-quarter comeback in a 34-24 win.
